snippet.title: Arcade Game: River Patrol (1981 Orca)
snippet.description: A boat driving game. You are the captain of a river patrol ship in this top-down game. Your mission : To save the poor souls who fell into the river. But it is not that easy, in your way lays some big boulders, crocodiles and some tree logs, all waiting to sink your vessel.
